      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIVERBANK MISS (4) finished third (17.98) two back at Richmond Straight but out of the placings last time when 6th there. Form here at this distance is sound. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. WICKED RAVEN (1) finds it hard to break through. Filled a minor placings again last time when third (18.48) at this track making it three placings in a row. Has a strong record from this draw, notching two wins and five minor placings from seven starts. Must be included in calculations. WOW IT'S ME (2) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 7th at this track in Grade 5 company. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Strong form has emerged from her last run. A big run wouldn't surprise. CLASSIC TEARS (8) is not to be discarded.",
